content: affaan-m: Merged two PRs this month, including a significant update to the web search plugin export (#1688) that added 10,765 lines while removing 1,742 lines, and a smaller update to the bootstrap plugin export (#1836) with 213 additions and 204 deletions. Has one open PR (#1689) also related to web search plugin export updates. Activity was sporadic, contributing on only 2 days this month, with primary focus on bugfix work (67%).
